<doc id="3378" url="https://en.wikinews.org/wiki?curid=3378" title="Russian diplomats operated string of brothels in Finland">
<h1>Russian diplomats operated string of brothels in Finland</h1>
&lt;strong class="published"&gt;&lt;span id="publishDate" class="value-title" title=""&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class="Z3988" style="display:none" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rfr_id=rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikinews.org:User%3ADendodge&amp;rft_id=info:sid/en.wikinews.org:&amp;rft.atitle=Russian%20diplomats%20operated%20string%20of%20brothels%20in%20Finland&amp;rft.jtitle=Wikinews&amp;rft.date=&amp;rft.aucorp=Wikinews+contributors&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.rights=CC-BY+2.5&amp;rft.identifier=&amp;rft.artnum="&gt; &lt;/span&gt; 

Diplomats at the Trade Representation of the Russian embassy have for a number of years operated at least 8 brothels in the Finnish capital.
The police investigation, which has just been completed, revealed that the diplomats were planning to expand their operation. They even planned to open a large hotel. 

About 100 Russian prostitutes worked at the brothels, and the diplomats are known to have pocketed more than $200,000. The police have not been able to interrogate the diplomats because of their diplomatic immunity. They left Finland soon after the police investigation began last spring.

<h2>References</h2>
<ul>
BULLET::::- Stefan Lundberg. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.hbl.fi/cgi-bin/mediaweb%3FNewsp%3Dhbl%26amp%3BDate%3D050120%26amp%3BModel%3Djuttu.html%26amp%3Bdepa%3Dinrikes%26amp%3Bstory%3D07422364.txt"&gt;Rysk jättebordell planerades i Helsingfors(Russian giant brothel planned in Helsinki)&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AHufvudstadsbladet"&gt;Hufvudstadsbladet&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, January 20, 2005
BULLET::::- Stefan Lundberg. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.hbl.fi/cgi-bin/mediaweb%3FNewsp%3Dhbl%26amp%3BDate%3D050120%26amp%3BModel%3Djuttu.html%26amp%3Bdepa%3Dinrikes%26amp%3Bstory%3D07422364.txt"&gt;Diplomathallickarna gömmer sig för polisen (Diplomat pimps hide from police)&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AHufvudstadsbladet"&gt;Hufvudstadsbladet&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, Dec 12, 2004

