BULLET::::- Tim Grieve. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.salon.com/news/feature/2005/01/20/boxer/index.html"&gt;Boxer's rebellion&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ASalon.com"&gt;Salon.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, January 20, 2005
BULLET::::- Carolyn Lochhead. "&lt;a href="http%3A//sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi%3Ff%3D/c/a/2005/01/20/RICE.TMP"&gt;Dems seek Senate debate on Rice Panel votes approval, but Boxer pushes to extend discussion&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ASan%20Francisco%20Chronicle"&gt;San Francisco Chronicle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, January 20, 2005

