BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/4190699.stm"&gt;US right attacks SpongeBob video&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABBC%20News%20Online"&gt;BBC News Online&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, January 20, 2005
