<doc id="3481" url="https://en.wikinews.org/wiki?curid=3481" title="UK freedom of information acts come into effect">
<h1>UK freedom of information acts come into effect</h1>
&lt;strong class="published"&gt;&lt;span id="publishDate" class="value-title" title=""&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class="Z3988" style="display:none" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rfr_id=rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikinews.org:User%3ADendodge&amp;rft_id=info:sid/en.wikinews.org:&amp;rft.atitle=UK%20freedom%20of%20information%20acts%20come%20into%20effect&amp;rft.jtitle=Wikinews&amp;rft.date=&amp;rft.aucorp=Wikinews+contributors&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.rights=CC-BY+2.5&amp;rft.identifier=&amp;rft.artnum="&gt; &lt;/span&gt; 

At the beginning of the calendar year 2005, the &lt;a href="w%3AUnited%20Kingdom"&gt;United Kingdom&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="w%3AFreedom%20of%20Information%20Act%20%28United%20Kingdom%29"&gt;Freedom of Information Act&lt;/a&gt; went into effect. The act of parliament should allow all citizens of the United Kingdom the freedom to investigate their own records or any data gathered by the government which might affect their lives. However, many within the government have stated that the act will not allow data of importance to national security to be accessed.

The act follows well-received acts in other countries. See &lt;a href="w%3AFreedom%20of%20Information%20Act"&gt;Freedom of Information Act&lt;/a&gt; on Wikipedia for more background on the history.

<h3>References</h3>

<ul>
BULLET::::- Robert Barr. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.mercurynews.com/mld/mercurynews/news/world/10561248.htm%3F1c"&gt;UK Freedom of Information Act Takes Effect&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Mercury%20News"&gt;The Mercury News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, January 04, 2005
BULLET::::- Jan Jun. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.eubusiness.com/EUnews/info.2005-01-16"&gt;UK Freedom of Information Act holds promise for postcommunist democracies&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AEUbusiness"&gt;EUbusiness&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, January 16, 2005
