BULLET::::- John Tilak. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.dmeurope.com/default.asp%3FArticleID%3D5535"&gt;Teliasonera Sweden quadruples GSM network speed, increases network coverage&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ADigital%20Media%20Europe"&gt;Digital Media Europe&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, January 22, 2005

