BULLET::::- &lt;a href="Associated%20Press"&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;. "&lt;a href="http%3A//story.news.yahoo.com/news%3Ftmpl%3Dstory%26amp%3Bcid%3D542%26amp%3Be%3D19%26amp%3Bu%3D/ap/fbi_openness"&gt;FBI Fights for Limited Document Searches&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AYahoo%21%20News"&gt;Yahoo! News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, January 25, 2005
BULLET::::- Michael J. Sniffen (&lt;a href="Associated%20Press"&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;). "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.cleveland.com/news/plaindealer/index.ssf%3F/base/news/1106397024153060.xml"&gt;Court ruling could lessen public access to FBI records&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3Acleaveland.com"&gt;cleaveland.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, January 22, 2005
