BULLET::::- Donna Miles. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.defenselink.mil/news/Jan2005/n01252005_2005012511.html"&gt;Bush Administration to Request $80 Billion Supplemental&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAmerican%20Forces%20Press%20Service"&gt;American Forces Press Service&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, January 26, 2005

</ul>
