BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.un.org/apps/news/story.asp%3FNewsID%3D13157%26amp%3BCr%3Dsudan%26amp%3BCr1%3D"&gt;Dozens of casualties in bombing raid on village in Sudan's Darfur region reported to UN&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AUN"&gt;UN&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, January 27, 2005
