<ul>
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.gio.gov.tw/taiwan-website/4-oa/20050128/2005012801.html"&gt;The ROC Government's Position on the 2005 Lunar New Year Cross-Strait Charter Flights&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AMainland%20Affairs%20Council%2C%20Executive%20Yuan"&gt;Mainland Affairs Council, Executive Yuan&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, January 29, 2005
BULLET::::- Luis Ramirez. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.voanews.com/english/2005-01-29-voa15.cfm"&gt;Direct Flights between China and Taiwan Take Off for First Time in 56 Years&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AVOICE%20OF%20AMERICA"&gt;VOICE OF AMERICA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, January 29, 2005
