BULLET::::- Lillian Saleh. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.thesundaymail.news.com.au/common/story_page/0%2C5936%2C12100309%25255E421%2C00.html"&gt;Drastic surgery on wrong patients&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Sunday%20Mail"&gt;The Sunday Mail&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, January 31, 2005
