BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/4227835.stm"&gt;US convinced of Darfur 'genocide'&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABBC"&gt;BBC&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, January 31, 2005
BULLET::::- Madeline Morri. "&lt;a href="http%3A//usinfo.state.gov/dhr/Archive/2003/Oct/15-823755.html"&gt;Judgment Without Democracy&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AWashington%20Post"&gt;Washington Post&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 24, 2002

</ul>


