BULLET::::- Jim Wagner, Michael Singer. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.internetnews.com/dev-news/article.php/3466751"&gt;Open Source Law Center Opens Doors&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3Awww.internetnews.com"&gt;www.internetnews.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 1, 2005
BULLET::::- Lonn Johnston. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.softwarefreedom.org/press-release-050201.html"&gt;New Law Center Founded to Assist Open Source Developers&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3Awww.softwarefreedom.org"&gt;www.softwarefreedom.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 1, 2005

