BULLET::::- Steven Lee Myers. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.nytimes.com/2005/02/03/international/europe/03cnd-geor.html"&gt;Apparent Gas Leak Kills Prime Minister of Georgia&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ANew%20York%20Times"&gt;New York Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 3, 2005
