BULLET::::- Judith Crosson. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.planetark.com/dailynewsstory.cfm/newsid/28848/story.htm"&gt;Once-Hated Grey Wolf Thrives in the US Rockies&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3APlanet%20Ark"&gt;Planet Ark&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, January 7, 2005
BULLET::::- &lt;a href="http%3A//www.defenders.org/releases/pr2005/pr020105b.html"&gt;Defenders of Wildlife&lt;/a&gt;, February 1, 2005

</ul>


