BULLET::::- Christine Kearney. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.reuters.com/newsArticle.jhtml%3Ftype%3DtopNews%26amp%3BstoryID%3D7545696"&gt;NY Court Says Gay Couples Have Equal Right to Marry&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AReuters"&gt;Reuters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 4, 2005
