BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.un.org/apps/news/story.asp%3FNewsID%3D13261%26amp%3BCr%3D%26amp%3BCr1%3D"&gt;Annan calls on Togolese to respect own constitution in appointing presidential successor&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AUN%20News"&gt;UN News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 7, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/africa/4241001.stm"&gt;Togo succession 'coup' denounced&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABBC%20News"&gt;BBC News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 6, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.un.org/apps/news/story.asp%3FNewsID%3D13251%26amp%3BCr%3DTogo%26amp%3BCr1%3D"&gt;Annan pays tribute to late Togolese President Gnassingbe Eyadema&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AUN%20News"&gt;UN News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 6, 2005
