BULLET::::- Andreea Pocotila. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.daily-news.ro/article_detail.php%3Fidarticle%3D5737"&gt;Lunar New Year's Eve celebrated in Bucharest&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABucharest%20Daily%20News"&gt;Bucharest Daily News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 7, 2005

