BULLET::::- &lt;a href="http%3A//www.city.kobe.jp/cityoffice/15/020/quake/"&gt;Disaster of Kobe City - Kobe City Hall&lt;/a&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;a href="http%3A//www.city.kobe.jp/cityoffice/06/013/kensyou_15/saisyuuhoukoku/anzen/2-4-3tosikiban.pdf"&gt;City Infrastructure for Safety - Kobe City Hall&lt;/a&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;a href="http%3A//www.reuters.co.uk/newsArticle.jhtml%3Ftype%3DworldNews%26amp%3BstoryID%3D655116"&gt;Kobe remembers quake dead - Reuters&lt;/a&gt;, by Elaine Lies
