BULLET::::- U.S. Commission on Civil Rights. "&lt;a href="http%3A//academic.udayton.edu/race/02rights/bush04Record.pdf"&gt;Redefining Rights in America: The Civil Rights Record of the George W. Bush Administration 2001-2004(draft)&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AU.S%20office%20of%20Civil%20Rights"&gt;U.S office of Civil Rights&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, September 2004
