BULLET::::- Allison Dunfield. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.theglobeandmail.com/servlet/story/RTGAM.20050210.w4martin0210/BNStory/National/"&gt;Not involved in sponsorship workings, Martin testifies&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AGlobe%20and%20Mail"&gt;Globe and Mail&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, Thursday, February 10, 2005 Updated at 3:18 PM EST
BULLET::::- Clifford Krauss. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.nytimes.com/2005/02/11/international/americas/11canada.html"&gt;Canadian Premier Testifies in Inquiry Into Quebec Payoff Scandal&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ANew%20York%20Times"&gt;New York Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 11, 2005

