BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.pfizer.com/are/news_releases/2005pr/mn_2005_0210.html"&gt;Pfizer and Microsoft target sellers of illegal Viagra and international spam rings&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3APfizer%20news%20release"&gt;Pfizer news release&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 10, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.microsoft.com/presspass/features/2005/feb05/02-10Pfizer.asp"&gt;Q&amp;A: Pfizer and Microsoft strike at alleged spammers&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AMicrosoft%20press%20release"&gt;Microsoft press release&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 10, 2005

