BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news10now.com/content/top_stories/default.asp%3FArID%3D36848"&gt;Gunmen open fire at Albany area mall&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ANews%2010%20Now"&gt;News 10 Now&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 13, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.in-forum.com/ap/index.cfm%3Fpage%3Dview%26amp%3Bid%3DD887TO9O0"&gt;Gunmen Open Fire at N.Y. Mall; 1 Injured&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAssociated%20Press"&gt;Associated Press&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 13, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.reuters.com/newsArticle.jhtml%3Ftype%3DdomesticNews%26amp%3BstoryID%3D7613002"&gt;Suspect Caught After Gunfire at NY Shopping Mall&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AReuters"&gt;Reuters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 13, 2005
