BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.xinhuanet.com/english/2005-02/15/content_2579519.htm"&gt;State Council sends work team to Liaoning coal blast site&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AXinhua"&gt;Xinhua&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 15, 2005
