BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.cnn.com/2005/ALLPOLITICS/02/09/white.house.reporter/index.html"&gt;White House reporter's credentials questioned&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACNN"&gt;CNN&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 10, 2005
BULLET::::- Jemima Kiss. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.journalism.co.uk/news/story1253.shtml"&gt;Fake White House correspondent unmasked by bloggers&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3Ajournalism.co.uk"&gt;journalism.co.uk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 12, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.foxnews.com/story/0%2C2933%2C147087%2C00.html"&gt;White House Reporter Using Fake Name Quits&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AFox%20news"&gt;Fox news&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 12, 2005
BULLET::::- SusanG. "&lt;a href="http%3A//wolverinetom.dailykos.com/user/SusanG"&gt;Plame &amp; Propagannon&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ADaily%20Kos"&gt;Daily Kos&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 9-10, 2005

