BULLET::::- &lt;a href="http%3A//nycgates.blogspot.com/"&gt;The Gates @ Central Park&lt;/a&gt; A community blog on which anyone may post comments about The Gates via email or mobile phone.
BULLET::::- &lt;a href="http%3A//www.geocities.com/qubestrader/TheGates.html"&gt;The Gates - Art Work&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span style="font-family: sans-serif; cursor: default; color: #0000CD; font-size: 1.2em; font-weight: bold;" title="This source has been taken offline but was used in the creation of this article before it went offline."&gt;(&lt;span class="video_source" style="color: #FF3300;font-size: 0.7em; position: relative; bottom: 0.1em"&gt;Source link broken&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
