BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.ananova.com/news/story/sm_1286285.html"&gt;Hunting ban challenge fails&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAnanova"&gt;Ananova&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 16, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.telegraph.co.uk/news/main.jhtml%3Fxml%3D/news/2005/02/16/uhunt.xml%26amp%3BsSheet%3D/portal/2005/02/16/ixportaltop.html"&gt;Pro-hunters lose latest challenge against ban&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Daily%20Telegraph%20%28United%20Kingdom%29"&gt;The Daily Telegraph (United Kingdom)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 16, 2005 (registration required)
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.timesonline.co.uk/article/0%2C%2C2-1486722%2C00.html"&gt;Appeal Court rules that hunting ban can go ahead&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Times"&gt;The Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 16, 2005
